"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-paralympics-schedule-days-times-paris-2024-b2599009.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Dates and times of all the events across 11 days of action in Paris this summer  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999981299667274, \"rank\": 1.8700366985344643e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  The 2024Paralympicsin Paris officially begins with the opening ceremony on Wednesday 28 August, kicking off 11 days of competition which comes to an end on 8 September.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999981299667274, \"rank\": 1.8700366985344643e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympics will feature 22 sports in 23 disciplines, with a total of 549 events across 11 days.\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are the traditional draws such as swimming, basketball, tennis and athletics.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There will not be any new disciplines at theParis 2024Paralympics, but badminton will be making only its second appearance.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 906, \"entiti